OL,3,CPaedophile prisoner left with access
OL,4,Cto kids in hospital, worker alleges
OL,6,FA healthcare worker has told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat a paedophile prisoner was allowed
OL,8,Fto be in close proximity to children
OL,9,Fwhilst being treated at Guernsey's
OL,10,FPrincess Elizabeth Hospital.
OL,12,FThe allegations include that he waved
OL,13,Fat children just metres away from his
OL,14,Fprivate room.
OL,16,FThe healthcare worker does not wish to
OL,17,Fbe identified but was so concerned
OL,18,Fwith the lack of security that they
OL,19,Fhave decided to speak out.
