OL,3,CPaedophile prisoner left with access
OL,4,Cto kids in hospital, worker alleges
OL,6,FThey claim: "A prison officer was with
OL,7,Fhim in the first instance. But after
OL,8,Ftreatment, he was left without an
OL,9,Fescort - the reason provided was that
OL,10,Fhe was essentially immobile.
OL,12,F"However, following physio treatment,
OL,13,Fhe was taking himself to the toilet
OL,14,Fand walking around, but his private
OL,15,Froom wasn't locked and he had access
OL,16,Fto an open ward.
OL,18,F"There were no physical restraints and
OL,19,Fno prison guards at all during the
OL,20,Ftime.
