OL,3,CPaedophile prisoner left with access
OL,4,Cto kids in hospital, worker alleges
OL,6,F"During a weekend when visitors could
OL,7,Ffreely come and go, a young family
OL,8,Fpassed his room, and he stood up and
OL,9,Fwaved at the children."
OL,11,FWhen a prisoner is moved to Guernsey's
OL,12,Fhospital for treatment, risk
OL,13,Fassessments must be carried out, the
OL,14,Fnumber of escorts chosen, and
OL,15,Fhealthcare staff should be informed of
OL,16,Fthe inmate's offending history,
OL,17,Fincluding any requirements.
