OL,3,CPaedophile prisoner left with access
OL,4,Cto kids in hospital, worker alleges
OL,6,FIn a statement, Deputy Marc
OL,7,FLeadbeater, President of the island's
OL,8,FHome Affairs Committee, said: "I am
OL,9,Freassured that the safeguards put in
OL,10,Fplace by the Prison Service in the
OL,11,Fhospital were appropriate to manage
OL,12,Fany potential risk.
OL,14,F"This included the fact that the
OL,15,Findividual was accommodated in a
OL,16,Fsingle room to minimise any
OL,17,Finteraction with the public, and
OL,18,Fneeded assistance to move around.
