OL,3,CPaedophile prisoner left with access
OL,4,Cto kids in hospital, worker alleges
OL,6,F"We have not been made aware of any
OL,7,Finappropriate interactions or
OL,8,Fincidents, and the management of the
OL,9,Fprisoner in hospital is believed to
OL,10,Fhave been successful."
OL,12,FThe inmate has since passed away and,
OL,13,Ffollowing the procedure for any
OL,14,Fprisoner's death in Guernsey, there
OL,15,Fwill now be a review into the
OL,16,Fprotocols followed.
OL,18,FThe concerns raised will form part of
OL,19,Fthis investigation.
